  <!-- ========== FAQ ========== -->
  <section class="section faq-section" id="faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions about ecommerce AI search optimisation in Singapore">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
        <h2>Ecommerce AI Search Optimisation Questions Answered</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d1">
          <summary>Why do ecommerce stores need AI search optimisation?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Shoppers increasingly ask AI platforms like ChatGPT and Gemini for product and store recommendations before making purchases. If your online store isn't in those AI answers, you're losing high-intent buyers to competitors that AI does recommend. AI-referred traffic converts at 4.4x the rate of traditional search traffic.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d2">
          <summary>How is ecommerce GEO different from regular ecommerce SEO?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Ecommerce SEO focuses on ranking product pages in Google search results. Ecommerce GEO ensures AI platforms recommend your store when shoppers ask questions like "best online store for sneakers in Singapore". The overlap between Google rankings and AI citations is below 20%, so strong Google rankings alone won't get you into AI recommendations.</p></div>
